{"tid":2076151,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警稱不分政治立場處理的士司機撞人案 袁海文批「扮公正」嘔心","createTime":"2020-06-23T10:04:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T10:59:45.000Z","uid":56115,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"36af47f073b34d1f94864dc2c293a7ab51b9d9f6","tid":2076151,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T10:04:29.000Z","msg":"（獨媒特約報導）深水埗區議會今早開會，區議員兼大律師劉偉聰要求警方交代，去年10月的深水埗的士司機鄭國泉撞人的調查進度。深水埗警區指揮官何啟軒稱，該宗<span style=\"color: red;\">「交通意外」已交商業罪案調查科跟進</span>，重申會不分政治立場處理案件；但案件正在調查中，不宜公開討論。民主黨袁海文批評警方的說法扮公正，至今卻仍沒有任何人被捕，形容十分嘔心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1074827\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1074827&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JYeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=86c3a266\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1074827&h=1118e480\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1074827</a>"},{"pid":"02cfb10180bebfa44cd38d5d7fbc5fff85f29d6a","tid":2076151,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T10:05:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d4c1d968e2f17d2c3055fedd6ba73fe0d788116","tid":2076151,"uid":25797,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T10:06:28.000Z","msg":"商業罪案調查科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbdc8a64cf28e786e02f88ef50b50a9b8ac77c8b","tid":2076151,"uid":56115,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T10:06:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AzrtXDs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAzrtXDs.jpg&h=844b8423&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"95afaf7b0840efccb18c10535e270670ebd64e62","tid":2076151,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T10:07:56.000Z","msg":"